title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8108.01 - City of Norwich
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8108.01 - City of Norwich

State Regulations
(a) Route 990L. Route 990L between Route 12 and the easterly Norwich city limit. (b) Route 12. The northbound and southbound
roadways of Route 12 between Route 990L and Borden Avenue, a distance of 0.9+-
mile in the City of Norwich. (c) Borden Avenue. The eastbound and westbound roadways of Borden Avenue between

Route 12 and the Victory Borden Avenue warehouse, a distance of 0.6+- mile in
the City of Norwich. (d) Prentice

Avenue. Prentice Avenue between Route 12 and O'Hara Drive. (e) O'Hara Drive. O'Hara Drive between

Prentice Avenue and its terminus, a distance of 0.15+- mile. Notes
